GUILTY plea entered to count 3, PTC theft.  Convicted.
The State moves to dismiss and read in counts 1 and 2.  Motion granted.
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years, consecutive to the jail sentence imposed on count 3 of 15 CF 396.
Conditions of probation:
1) no contact with Kevin Wasmer;
2) maintain fulltime employment, schooling or combination;
3) assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
4) pay court costs;
5) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
6) provide DNA sample;
7) pay restitution, joint and several with Kevin Wasmer.  $842.78 to Community First Credit Union, Att: Cindy Pierce at PO Box 1487, Appleton, WI 54912-1487 and $800.00 to Kristen Schmidt at 2934 S. 10th Street, Manitowoc, WI.  Restituiton is to be paid at the rate of $50.00 per month.
